messages.message: I’m wondering if the output of queries can be improved. I can ask questions, but the answers aren’t formatted in a way that’s easily transferrable.
Do you mean the answers are in natural language, vs. something that’s more structured like JSON or markdown? Are you in build mode or chat mode?
I did the build mode as well and it does have the export feature which I suppose is what I should be using
What kind of format did you expect the answers to be in?
maybe a table? But I’m trying all of this for the first time… so not really sure what I’m expecting
Still useful feedback! if you can give a concrete example of the question you asked, response you got, and what you expected, that’s useful as we plan out how to improve build mode (and chat mode)
For Chat this is work in progress! To improve the response rendering
